column2: The former Yugoslav Republic of Macedonia

column1: ll: Missing indicators on nutrition.kk: The HDRO specifications refer to somewhat modified definitions of deprivations in some indicators compared to the 2010 specifications. See Kovacevic and Calderon (2014) for details.mm: Refers to urban areas only oo: Missing indicator on child mortality.qq: Missing indicator on type of floor.pp: Missing indicator on cooking fuel.nn: Missing indicator on electricity. rr: Missing indicator on school attendance.
